title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOC.description: Allows an app to access location in the background. If you're requesting this permission, you must also request either

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.info: Allows an application to request installing packages.
android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.description: Malicious applications can use this to try and trick users into installing additional malicious packages.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

FCS_RBG_EXT.1.1.choice: The application invoke platform-provided DRBG functionality for its cryptographic operations.

FCS_STO_EXT.1.1.choice: The application does not store any credentials to non-volatile memory.

FCS_CKM_EXT.1.1.choice: The application generate no asymmetric cryptographic keys.

FDP_DEC_EXT.1.1.choice: The application has access to ['location', 'network connectivity'].

FDP_DEC_EXT.1.2.choice: The application has access to ['system logs'].

FDP_NET_EXT.1.1.choice: The application has user/application initiated network communications.

FDP_DAR_EXT.1.1.choice: The application implement functionality to encrypt sensitive data in non-volatile memory.

FMT_MEC_EXT.1.1.choice: The application invoke the mechanisms recommended by the platform vendor for storing and setting configuration options.

FTP_DIT_EXT.1.1.choice: The application does encrypt some transmitted data with HTTPS/TLS/SSH between itself and another trusted IT product.

FCS_RBG_EXT.2.1,FCS_RBG_EXT.2.2.choice: The application perform all deterministic random bit generation (DRBG) services in accordance with NIST Special Publication 800-90A using Hash_DRBG. The deterministic RBG is seeded by an entropy source that accumulates entropy from a platform-based DRBG and a software-based noise source, with a minimum of 256 bits of entropy at least equal to the greatest security strength (according to NIST SP 800-57) of the keys and hashes that it will generate.

FCS_CKM.1.1(1).choice: The application generate asymmetric cryptographic keys not in accordance with FCS_CKM.1.1(1) using key generation algorithm RSA schemes and cryptographic key sizes of 1024-bit or lower.

FCS_COP.1.1(2).choice: The application perform cryptographic hashing services in accordance with a specified cryptographic algorithm SHA-1/SHA-256/SHA-384/SHA-512 and message digest sizes 160/256/384/512 bits.

FCS_COP.1.1(3).choice: The application perform cryptographic signature services (generation and verification) in accordance with a specified cryptographic algorithm RSA schemes using cryptographic key sizes of 2048-bit or greater.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.2.choice: The application implement HTTPS using TLS.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.3.choice: The application notify the user and not establish the connection or request application authorization to establish the connection if the peer certificate is deemed invalid.

FIA_X509_EXT.2.1.choice: The application use X.509v3 certificates as defined by RFC 5280 to support authentication for HTTPS , TLS.

"homepage_hero_desc" : "Blokada adalah aplikasi pemblokir iklan dan privasi yang populer untuk platform Android dan iOS. Aplikasi ini didukung dan dikembangkan secara aktif oleh komunitas open source yang luar biasa."
"homepage_community_cta_subheader" : "Присъединете се към нас и и кажете здравей!"
"payment_feature_desc_no_ads" : "Korzystaj ze słynnej technologii blokowania reklam Blokady, poprawiając poziom ochrony i dbając o prywatność Twoich danych."
"activity_empty_text" : "Essayez d'utiliser votre appareil et revenez ici plus tard pour voir à quel endroit votre périphérique se connecte."
"homepage_community_desc" : "Blokada 不僅是隱私應用程式。它也是關心數位隱私與福祉的人們所組成的社群。您可以在我們的論壇上找到我們，並可以在那裡詢問任何您想要問的問題。我們也在其他的社群媒體與聊天軟體上出現。"
"error_unknown" : "Ein unbekanntes Problem ist aufgetreten. Bitte versuche es erneut. Wenn das Problem weiterhin besteht, kontaktiere uns bitte, indem du oben auf das Hilfe-Symbol tippst."

"homepage_faq_desc_two" : "Blokada hindrar appar och webbläsare som är installerade på din enhet från att skicka din privata information (även kallat att spåra fingeravtryck) till Internet. Den krypterar också en del av din nätverksaktivitet (DNS-frågor). Om du behöver mer skydd får Blokada Plus din enhet att ansluta via vår VPN-tjänst och använder WireGuard®-protokollet för att kryptera all din nätverkstrafik."
"account_label_enter_to_continue" : "Въведете ID номер на профила за да продължите"
"error_account_inactive_after_restore" : "Ce compte ne semble pas être valide ou actif. Si vous pensez qu'il s'agit d'une erreur, contactez-nous en cliquant sur l'icône d'aide en haut de l'écran."

"homepage_faq_desc_three" : "Blokada Plus ist unser sicherer und moderner VPN-Dienst (Virtual Private Network). Hierbei kommt WireGuard® zum Einsatz - ein schnelles Protokoll mit erstklassiger Verschlüsselung und geringem Akkuverbrauch. Blokada Plus verschlüsselt alle deine Netzwerkaktivitäten in Echtzeit und bietet so den höchsten verfügbaren Schutz. Du erhältst auch die beliebten VPN-Funktionen - verbirg deine IP-Adresse, ändere deinen Standort und entsperre geobeschränkte Inhalte."
"error_payment_not_available" : "Betalingen zijn niet beschikbaar voor dit apparaat. Ofwel is Apple Pay niet geactiveerd, ofwel verwerken we nog geen aankopen in uw land."
"homepage_vpn_desc" : "究極のプライバシー保護のために、Blokada Plus にアップグレードし、VPN経由で接続できます。 最先端の VPN プロトコルである WireGuard® を使用して、ネットワークのアクティビティを暗号化し、IP アドレスを隠します。"

"homepage_faq_desc_three" : "Blokada Plus هي خدمة VPN (شبكة افتراضيّة خاصّة) آمنة و حديثة. يستخدم WireGuard® - وهو بروتوكول سريع مع تشفير هو الأفضل في فئته و استخدام منخفض للبطاريّة. يقوم Blokada Plus بتشفير جميع أنشطة الشبكة الخاصّة بك في الوقت الفعلي ، ممّا يمنحك أعلى مستوى من الحماية المتاحة. يمكنك أيضاً الحصول على ميّزات VPN الشائعة - إخفاء عنوان IP الخاصّ بك ، و تغيير موقعك ، و إلغاء حَظْر المحتوى المُقَيَّد جغرافياً."

"homepage_faq_desc_two" : "Blokada предотвращает отправку личных данных ( так называемых отпечатков) в интернет приложениями и браузерами, установленными на вашем устройстве. "intro_text" : "A blue ring means that Blokada is working.

Remember, some ads, like YouTube, cannot be blocked. However, you will notice a difference in many other apps.

We recommend you activate Always on VPN / Connect on Demand in your system settings."

"homepage_faq_desc_two" : "O Blokada impede que aplicativos e navegadores instalados no seu dispositivo enviem seus dados privados (conhecidos como rastreamento de impressões digitais) para a Internet. Ele também criptografa algumas das suas atividades de rede (consultas DNS). Se você precisar de mais proteção, o Blokada Plus faz seu dispositivo se conectar através de nossa VPN e usa o protocolo do WireGuard® para criptografar todo o tráfego de rede."

"homepage_faq_desc_two" : "Blokada brání aplikacím a prohlížečům nainstalovaným ve vašem zařízení v odesílání vašich soukromých dat (známých jako sledování otisků prstů) na internet. Šifruje také některé vaše síťové aktivity (dotazy DNS). Pokud potřebujete větší ochranu, Blokada Plus umožňuje připojení vašeho zařízení prostřednictvím naší VPN a k šifrování celého vašeho síťového provozu používá protokol WireGuard®."
"main_ask_for_permissions_description" : "Blokada is using a VPN Configuration to block ads. You will be asked to allow it in the next step."

"account_restore_description" : "Oroa dig inte, om du har förlorat eller glömt ditt konto-ID kan vi återställa det. Vänligen kontakta vår support och ge oss information som gör det möjligt för oss att identifiera ditt köp (t. ex. sista 4 siffrorna i ditt kreditkort, eller din e-post på PayPal)."

playstore_details.title: Blokada Slim Ad blocker - No Ads, better battery
playstore_details.description:
This is the only official app on Play Store from the Blokada open source project. Beware of clones, they may contain malicious code.

Blokada Slim Ad blocker is a free app that uses DNS (Domain Name System) servers to enable you to have an ad free browsing experience to see only the content you want.

There is also a built in VPN that is optional to use.

The website of the project is: https://blokada.org. The version from the website has more features and is also free.

Join us on our Telegram chat if you have questions or feedback: https://go.blokada.org/chat

----

Best features:
- NO root permissions required!
- Supports every web browser and apps.
- DNS based interception (VPN mode) for all modern browsers.
- Blocks sites that distribute malicious content, viruses and fraudulent websites.

The most compatible ad blocker on the market!

• ❎ Blocks ads
• 💰 Saves your data plan
• 🛵 Browse FASTER by loading less data
• 🔋 Increase battery life
